headline: Cognizant, Temenos team up for core banking solutions in Australia

headline: Cognizant's "Vibe Coding" Event Sets GUINNESS WORLD RECORDS™ Title
summary: Cognizant (NASDAQ: CTSH) has successfully completed its attempt for a GUINNESS WORLD RECORDS™ title for the most participants in an online generative AI hackathon. Over a ten-day period, 53,199 Cognizant associates across 40 countries took part in a Vibe Coding event, a global initiative designed to democratize innovation and build AI fluency at scale.
